text: Alki Larnaca was a football club from Cyprus. It was based in Larnaka. == Honours == Cyprus Football Association * Cypriot Cup Finalist: 5 (1967, 1970, 1976, 1977, 1980) * Cypriot Second Division championship: 4 (1960, 1982, 2001, 2010) ==References== Category:Cypriot football clubs
